column5: looks like its going to be a good year for Walleye ...all fish caught on small walker dipsys and 20 ft Trip-zs  with Fishmaster Harness 68 fow...go gett'em

Nice wallys Steve!!  We were near Pt Maitland Sunday trolling for wallys but probably not deep enough.  We were in 50 - 55 fow, marked a few but no takers.  Also tried for perch near the mouth of the river.  6 other boats & my boat - no perch being caught.
